      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNNY STRIDE (8) latest effort finished 2nd in a Grade 5 NP on June 1 over 390m at this track behind Compare Joe beaten 2 lengths (22.46). Looks suited here and rates on top. REV TREASURE (4) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when second and beaten half a length at this track over 390m in 22.40. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Well placed and gets her chance. BONE SHAKER (3) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (22.99) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Key player on best and worth another try. JARMON (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
